stateDiagram-v2
  direction LR
  [*] --> S_IDLE
  S_IDLE --> S_XOR: q_valid
  S_XOR --> S_ACC: XOR + mask one 64-bit word
  S_ACC --> S_XOR: w < 16 (next word)
